# DESCRIPTION
## Linear Algebra
## Problem 1.6.17 in Anton Elementary Linear Algebra, 9th edition
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## KEYWORDS('matrix')

## DBsubject('Linear Algebra')
## DBchapter('Systems of Linear Equations and Matrices')
## DBsection('Elimination Methods')
